      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start. One thing though, we've had some issues recently with the ground being a bit soft after the rain. What specific things should I look for regarding the foundation and the base to make sure the whole thing doesn't shift or collapse under load?",
